skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: mustang band
des: To use this skill, simply say "Alexa, ask Mustang Band what are my upcoming band events?" and Alexa will respond with details on the next Mustang Band calendar event. For example, Alexa might respond with "Football at UC Davis on October 28th, 2017".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
